<subSubSection id="C3216524FFD8FFA5FF43FB65FDF8F9FA" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8436AFFFD8FFA5FF43FB65FDF8F9FA" blockId="1.[136,1452,1268,1547]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFD8FFA5FF43FB65FF71FAFF" box="[136,186,1268,1294]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">This</collectorName>
original specimen mentioned in the protologue was collected in 
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFD8FFA5FC4CFB65FC00FAFF" box="[903,971,1268,1294]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">Bahia</collectorName>
, and it is preserved in 
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFD8FFA5FB0AFB65FA97FAFE" box="[1217,1372,1268,1295]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">Herbarium M</collectorName>
, which is cited by 
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFD8FFA5FECEFA89FE97FAC3" box="[261,348,1304,1330]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">Martius</collectorName>
as the place where his collections are located (
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFD8FFA5FCBBFA89FBC7FAC3" author="Martius, C. F. P. V." box="[880,1036,1304,1330]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" pagination="98 - 102" refId="ref7849" refString="Martius, C. F. P. V. (1826) XXXII Luhea Willd. Nova genera et species plantarum: quas in itinere per Brasiliam MDCCCXVII-MDCCCXX 1 (4): 98 - 102." type="journal article" year="1826">Martius 1826</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFD8FFA5FBDCFA89FAD6FAC3" author="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S." box="[1047,1309,1304,1330]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" refId="ref8497" refString="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S. (1976 - 1988) Taxonomic Literature: A selective guide to botanical publications and collections with dates, commentaries and types, 2 nd ed., Smithsonian Libraries, last updated 28 Jun. 2012. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 48631" type="book" year="1976">Stafleu &amp; Cowan 1976</bibRefCitation>
–1988: 325). 
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFD8FFA5FF43FAACFF54FAA6" box="[136,159,1341,1367]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">In</collectorName>
the absence of duplicates, we confirm 
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFD8FFA5FD92FAACFD2BFAA7" box="[601,736,1341,1366]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFD8FFA5FD92FAACFD79FAA7" box="[601,690,1341,1366]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">Martius</collectorName>
s.n.
</emphasis>
(M0210187) as the 
<typeStatus id="5480880DFFD8FFA5FC0DFAADFBE3FAA7" box="[966,1064,1340,1366]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFD8FFA5FB85FAACFB15FAA7" authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1826" box="[1102,1246,1340,1366]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="candicans">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFD8FFA5FB85FAACFB15FAA7" box="[1102,1246,1340,1366]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">L. candicans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Arts. 9.1 and 9.2 of the ICN), as also recognized by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFD8FFA5FDC7FAF1FD61FA8A" author="Cunha, M. C. S." box="[524,682,1376,1403]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" pagination="5 - 41" refId="ref7419" refString="Cunha, M. C. S. (1985) Revisao das especies do genero Luehea Willd. (Tiliaceae), ocorrentes no estado do Rio de Janeiro. Sellowia, Anais Botanicos do Herbario Barbosa Rodrigues 37: 5 - 41." type="journal article" year="1985">
<collectingCountry id="F32C763FFFD8FFA5FDC7FAF1FD9EFA8B" box="[524,597,1376,1402]" name="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">Cunha</collectingCountry>
(1985)
</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFD8FFA5FD7FFAF1FC78FA8A" author="Schumann, K." box="[692,947,1376,1403]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" pagination="117 - 200" refId="ref8376" refString="Schumann, K. (1886) Tilliaceae. Flora Brasiliensis, enumeratio plantarum in Brasilia hactenus detectarum: quas suis aliorumque botanicorum studiis descriptas et methodo naturali digestas partim icone illustratas 12 (3): 117 - 200. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 454" type="journal article" year="1886">Schumann (1886: 154)</bibRefCitation>
considered 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFD8FFA5FBF1FAF0FB02FA8B" authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1826" box="[1082,1225,1376,1402]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="candicans">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFD8FFA5FBF1FAF0FB02FA8B" box="[1082,1225,1376,1402]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">L. candicans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym for 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFD8FFA5FA5EFAF0FF29FA6F" authorityName="Saint-Hilaire" authorityYear="1828" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="uniflora">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFD8FFA5FA5EFAF0FF29FA6F" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">L. uniflora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFD8FFA5FF3BFA14FE93FA6E" box="[240,344,1413,1439]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">However</collectorName>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFD8FFA5FEA8FA14FDF8FA6E" author="Burret, K. E. M." box="[355,563,1412,1439]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" pagination="592 - 880" refId="ref7098" refString="Burret, K. E. M. (1926) Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Tiliaceen. Notizblatt des Botanischen Gartens und Museums zu Berlin-Dahlem 9 (88): 592 - 880. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 3994327" type="journal article" year="1926">Burret (1926: 826)</bibRefCitation>
recognized the priority of the name 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFD8FFA5FC0CFA14FB9DFA6F" authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1826" box="[967,1110,1412,1438]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="candicans">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFD8FFA5FC0CFA14FB9DFA6F" box="[967,1110,1412,1438]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">L. candicans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
over 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFD8FFA5FB5FFA14FAC0FA6F" authorityName="Saint-Hilaire" authorityYear="1828" box="[1172,1291,1412,1438]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="uniflora">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFD8FFA5FB5FFA14FAC0FA6F" box="[1172,1291,1412,1438]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">L. uniflora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as the former was correctly published in 1826 (
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFD8FFA5FDC1FA39FD28FA33" author="Martius, C. F. P. V." box="[522,739,1448,1474]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" pagination="98 - 102" refId="ref7849" refString="Martius, C. F. P. V. (1826) XXXII Luhea Willd. Nova genera et species plantarum: quas in itinere per Brasiliam MDCCCXVII-MDCCCXX 1 (4): 98 - 102." type="journal article" year="1826">Martius 1826: 102</bibRefCitation>
), while the latter was published two years later (
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFD8FFA5FAD2FA39FF37FA17" author="Saint-Hilaire, A." pageId="1" pageNumber="181" pagination="289 - 295" refId="ref8353" refString="Saint-Hilaire, A. (1828) LXVI Luhea Willd. Flora Brasiliae meridionalis 1 (8): 289 - 295." type="journal article" year="1828">Saint-Hilaire 1828: 291</bibRefCitation>
). 
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFD8FFA5FEC5FA5DFE99FA17" box="[270,338,1484,1510]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">Based</collectorName>
on 
<typeStatus id="5480880DFFD8FFA5FEB0FA5DFE16FA17" box="[379,477,1484,1510]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">holotype</typeStatus>
study, the application of the name 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFD8FFA5FC95FA5CFC26FA17" authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1826" box="[862,1005,1484,1510]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="candicans">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFD8FFA5FC95FA5CFC26FA17" box="[862,1005,1484,1510]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="181">L. candicans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is fully confirmed herein as an accepted species, as accepted by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFD8FFA5FE5AFA61FE11F9FB" author="Cunha, M. C. S." box="[401,474,1520,1546]" pageId="1" pageNumber="181" pagination="5 - 41" refId="ref7419" refString="Cunha, M. C. S. (1985) Revisao das especies do genero Luehea Willd. (Tiliaceae), ocorrentes no estado do Rio de Janeiro. Sellowia, Anais Botanicos do Herbario Barbosa Rodrigues 37: 5 - 41." type="journal article" year="1985">
